    "The maximum value is about 12µs.",
    "Even when factoring in the WCET of the timestamp function, the overhead can be deemed negligible.To measure the execution time for an input, the target program is executed multiple times.",
    "Specifically, in this study, the programs were run 10 times to measure their execution times under varying conditions.",
    "To mitigate the influence of outliers,the upper and lower limits were calculated for outlier detection based on the interquartile range (IQR) [109]:• Upper Limit = Q 3 + 1.5 × IQR • Lower Limit = Q 1 -1.5 × IQRWhere Q 3 and Q 1 are the third and first quartiles, respectively, and the IQR is defined as Q 3 -Q 1.",
    "Execution times falling outside these limits were considered outliers and removed from the dataset."
